"<b>Outprize</b>, owt-prīz′, <i>v.t.</i> (<i>Shak.</i>) to exceed in the value set upon it.",
"<b>Output</b>, owt′pōōt, <i>n.</i> the quantity of metal made by a smelting furnace, or of coal taken from a pit, within a certain time, production generally.",
